“今日最佳照片”里的医生，我们找到了。
Doctor in Best Picture Today. We found it.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 李佳蔚上海复旦大学附属中山医院官方微博 图3月5日，武大人民医院东院，上海复旦大学附属中山医院支援湖北医疗队队员刘凯医生在护送病人做CT的途中，停下来，让已经住院近一个月的87岁老先生欣赏了一次久违的日落。
Li Jia Wei Shanghai Fudan University affiliated Zhongshan Hospital official Weibo Chart March 5, Wu Da People's Hospital East Hospital, Shanghai Fudan University affiliated Zhongshan Hospital supported Hubei Medical Team member Dr. Liu Kai while escorting patients on CT.
落日余晖下的两个身影，病人和医生，这个温暖人心的瞬间被拍下来后，感动无数网友，被评为：今日最佳照片。
Two figures under the sunset, the patient and the doctor, this warm human moment was photographed, touched countless netizens, was rated as the best picture of today.
当天晚上，27岁的刘凯医生忙碌一天后回到房间，通过电话接受澎湃新闻记者采访，讲述了傍晚时分与老先生偶然欣赏夕阳的经过。
That night, the 27-year-old Dr. Liu Kai returned to his room after a busy day and gave a telephone interview to the roaring journalist, telling the story of an evening spent enjoying the sunset with the old gentleman.
这位87岁的老先生入院时是重症患者，在上海医疗团队的救治下，目前身体情况已不断转好。
The 87-year-old man was hospitalized with a serious illness and is now in good health thanks to the medical team in Shanghai.
今天下午四点多，刘凯推着他去做一个CT检查随访，在回病房的途中，和煦的夕阳恰好洒在病人和医生身上。
More than four this afternoon, Liu Kai pushed him to do a CT examination follow-up, on the way back to the ward, the genial sunset just sprinkled on the patient and the doctor.
“我看老先生挺高兴的，就问他要不要看一会（夕阳），他说好。
I thought the old gentleman was very happy, and asked him if he wanted to see the sunset. He said yes.
”于是两人停下来。
"So they both stopped.
刘凯说，对于老先生而言，他已经一个月没有看到阳光。
Mr. Liu said he hadn't seen the sun for a month.
其实对他自己来说，每天早出晚归，一直待在病房，也很少看到太阳。
For himself, he came home early and late every day, stayed in the ward, and rarely saw the sun.
所以当两人看到沐浴在夕阳下时，其实都挺高兴的。
So when they saw the sun bathed in the sun, in fact are quite happy.
“您觉得怎么样？”停下后，刘凯问老先生，后者答，“夕阳蛮好。
"What do you think?" When he stopped, Liu Kai asked the old man, who replied, "The sunset is fine.
”看了三四分钟，刘凯知道这个老先生的病情还不稳定，室外温度不高，就推着他回到病房。
"After watching for three or four minutes, Liu Kai knew that the old man was still unwell and that the outdoor temperature was not high.
刘凯说，回去后老先生心情很好，很快入睡休息了。
Liu Kai said that the old man was in a good mood after his return and fell asleep quickly.
刘凯医生是中山医院第四批支援湖北医疗队队员，自2月7日起他们一直在武汉前线奋战。
Dr Liu Kai is a member of the 4th Support Hubei Medical Team at Zhongshan Hospital. They have been fighting in Wuhan since February 7.
上海医疗队刚去时，这位老先生病情很重，对所有人不理不睬。
When the Shanghai medical team first went, the old man was very ill and paid no attention to anyone.
老先生的家人住的很远，武汉全城的交通停运，家人来送东西很不容易，中山医院医疗队便承包了所有的生活照料。
The old gentleman's family lives far away, Wuhan whole city traffic is stopped, the family comes to deliver things very not easy, Zhongshan hospital medical team contracted all the living care.
糕点、水果、各类生活用品、营养品，都送到老先生以及其他病人手中。
Cake, fruit, all kinds of daily necessities, nutrition, are sent to the old gentleman and other patients.
20多天的相处下来，老先生不但病情越来越好，和医护人员的关系也越发融洽。
After more than 20 days together, the old man is getting better and better, and the relationship with the medical staff is becoming more harmonious.
中山医院医疗团队负责的是武大人民医院东院20和22两个病区，患者皆是重症及危重患者。
The medical team of Zhongshan Hospital is in charge of the 20 and 22 wards of the East Hospital of Wudang People's Hospital.
“现在绝大部分患者病情已经稳定下来，有一些患者已经出院。
"The vast majority of patients have stabilized and some have been discharged," he said.
”刘凯说。
"said Liu Kai.
有个重症病人，最近已经转为轻症，马上要出院了，他就把所有医护人员的名字都记在了一张纸上。
One serious patient, who had recently turned mild and was about to be discharged from hospital, wrote down the names of all the paramedics on a piece of paper.
还有许多病人出院时告诉这些上海医护人员们：等疫情过去，请大家吃热干面。
Many patients left the hospital to tell the Shanghai medical personnel: When the epidemic is over, please eat hot-and-dry noodles.
